      <title>银行、直接贷款机构在并购交易转换后关注 Iris 再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/banks-direct-lenders-eye-iris-refinancing-after-m-a-deal-switch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于 Iris Software 的私募股权所有者将较小的股份出售给其他买家，因此错失了提供收购融资的机会，银行和直接贷款机构正准备就 Iris Software 的债务再融资展开竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/banks-direct-lenders-eye-iris-refinancing-after-m-a-deal-switch</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:35:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
